      <h1>Legal estate &amp; title</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        The legal layer of the property pack — who owns it, on what tenure,
        what the title register records, and what binds the estate. This is
        the largest cluster in the PDTF schema; it splits into seven
        sub-pages by object sub-cluster.
      </p>

      <aside class="callout callout--key" role="note">
        <p class="callout__label">The shape of this cluster</p>
        <p>
          Tenure governs the conveyance. Title — registered with HMLR —
          carries the seal of state behind every ownership claim and every
          charge or restriction over the estate. Ownership describes <em>how</em>
          the seller holds the estate and <em>what</em> they transfer at completion
          (freehold, leasehold, managed). Boundaries and rights complete
          the legal envelope.
        </p>
      </aside>

      <h2 id="subpages">Pages in this cluster</h2>
      <ul class="cluster-index">
        <li><a href="/schema/legal-estate/tenure"><strong>Tenure</strong></a> — freehold/leasehold/commonhold marketing tenure and the legal-owner roster.</li>
        <li><a href="/schema/legal-estate/title/oc-summary"><strong>Title — Official Copy summary</strong></a> — parsed OC summary: proprietorship, lease, charges, restrictions, notices.</li>
        <li><a href="/schema/legal-estate/title/oc-full"><strong>Title — Official Copy full register</strong></a> — raw register data and additional title documents.</li>
        <li><a href="/schema/legal-estate/ownership/freehold"><strong>Ownership — freehold transfer</strong></a> — what's transferred when the estate is freehold.</li>
        <li><a href="/schema/legal-estate/ownership/leasehold"><strong>Ownership — leasehold transfer</strong></a> — lease term, ground rent, service charge, management, consents.</li>
        <li><a href="/schema/legal-estate/ownership/managed"><strong>Ownership — managed</strong></a> — managed freehold / commonhold contacts, finances, disputes.</li>
        <li><a href="/schema/legal-estate/boundaries-rights"><strong>Boundaries &amp; rights</strong></a> — legal boundaries and informal arrangements over the estate.</li>
      </ul>
</Layout>
